      <prop type="x-translation-ref">噫嘻.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>噫嘻成王，既昭假爾，率時農夫，播厥百穀。
駿發爾私，終三十里，亦服爾耕，十千維耦。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Oh! yes, king Khăng
Brightly brought himself near.
Lead your husbandmen
To sow their various kinds of grain,
Going vigorously to work ​on your private fields,
All over the thirty lî.
Attend to your ploughing,
With your ten thousand men all in pairs.</seg>
      </tuv>
